title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.01.08
description:
STEVE ATTACKS AN ATTACKER:

Janis is in an abusive relationship, and she wants Steve&#039;s help to get out of it. Janis&#039;s boyfriend, Dwight, admits to putting his hands on Janis and her child! Steve has a place for Janis to go at the end of the show if she decides to leave Dwight. Steve helps Janis stand up for herself and tell Dwight what she really wants to say!
